data.description: OPEN HOUSE FEB. 17TH 12PM TO 2PM. If you’ve been looking for the perfect 3 Bed, 3 Bath, 2 Car garage home with low maintenance living, this is the home for you! This one owner ranch villa has been meticulously maintained and The open floor plan on the main level features vaulted ceilings, a fireplace, tons of natural light and main floor laundry. The spacious kitchen offers ample cabinet space, countertop seating and stainless steel appliances. Primary Bedroom has large walk-in closet, 3/4 bath with dual sinks and plenty of room for a king-sized bed. The walkout lower level provides a spacious living area, with a third bedroom and bathroom. Plus a Huge utility room and driveway expansion! The HOA covers lawn care, fertilizer treatments, snow removal, exterior painting, and sprinkler system maintenance. Don't miss this incredible opportunity for a carefree lifestyle in an unbeatable location! Close to shopping, Offutt AFB and easy access to Hwy 75, 370, and Cornhusker Road.
